[Though the odds that the above 3 events are related to AI are rather
remote, they are posted for 2 main reasons: to commend the relevant
authorities for their justified alertness and to request the outcome
of the investigations.
It would also help if general statements on death in "birds" include
species names. The same need for specificity is applicable to
statements on "toxic water" or "toxic elements." - Mod.AS]
